## GET /api/products/{id}

Scenario 12 (single-item view).

Request:
```json
GET /api/products/10000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000002
```

Response — 200 OK (CAT-007: zero stock, still visible):
```json
{
  "id": "10000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000002",
  "name": "Insulated Steel Bottle",
  "description": "750ml double-wall insulated bottle.",
  "category": "Home & Kitchen",
  "unitPrice": "24.50",
  "inStock": false
}
```

Response — 404 Not Found (CAT-008: a Deactivated product is treated as if
it doesn't exist to a browsing customer — not a 403, since its existence
itself isn't meant to be visible):
```json
{
  "error": {
    "code": "PRODUCT_NOT_FOUND",
    "message": "No product with this id."
  }
}
```

