## Regression check against Phase 1/2

- No identity endpoint's shape changes. The only interaction is the
  Authorization header on POST /api/products — a Deactivated admin
  account (Phase 2, scenario 7) must get the same 401 from Kong as any
  other Deactivated account attempting an authenticated call, before this
  service ever sees the request.
